.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, french, japanese, thai, spanish, argentine, chinese
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse, goldfish, ferret, snake, dog, frog
 1. the spanish is on the left of the australian##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the owner of the snake is the chinese##1
 4. the japanese is on the left of the argentine##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 6. the thai is the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the australian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the frog and the thai##2
 9. the australian is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the french is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish | australian | french   | thai | japanese | argentine |
| Pet           | snake | dog     | mouse     | goldfish | ferret   | guinea-pig   | frog    |

