.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, milk, 7up, soy-milk, cola, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: british, american, japanese, thai, german, french, brazilian
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the japanese##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the german##1
 3. the french is on the right of the thai##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the german##1
 5. the british is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the thai is between the person drinking milk and the french##2
 7. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
 8. the thai is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the american##1
10. the british is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | milk    | soy-milk  | 7up  | coffee  | almond-milk      | cola       | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | german | thai | french | brazilian | british | japanese | american  |

