.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, reggae, dubstep, funk, jazz, r&b, hip-hop
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, tram, scooter, car, bus, taxi
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the car is the fan of reggae##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of electronic##2
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
7. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
8. the person driving the subway is the fan of funk##1
9. the fan of jazz is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | jazz | electronic | dubstep | hip-hop      | reggae      | r&b |
| Transport     | subway | bus | taxi       | snowmobile | tram | car | scooter |

