.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, musician, dressmaker, entrepreneur, social-worker, designer, manager
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, tennis, volleyball, soccer, golf, basketball, baseball
1. the dressmaker is on the left of the manager##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the social-worker##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the musician is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the designer is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is golf and the software-developer##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
8. the designer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | social-worker | software-developer | entrepreneur | designer | musician | dressmaker     | manager |
| Sport   | volleyball   | soccer    | baseball    | golf      | tennis  | biathlon | basketball |

