.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, tea, mirinda, soy-milk, water, sprite
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, climbing, badminton, golf, lacrosse, swimming, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person drinking soy-milk##2
10. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice    | mirinda | tea   | water | sprite    | soy-milk |
| Sport      | golf | sailing | tennis    | climbing | lacrosse    | badminton | swimming  |

