.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, 7up, almond-milk, soy-milk, iced-tea, milk
The people have 7 different jobs:  nurse, doctor, lawyer, security-guard, electrician, dancer, paramedic
 1. the electrician is on the left of the security-guard##1
 2. the nurse is on the left of the lawyer##1
 3. the dancer is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the electrician is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking milk##2
 7. the doctor is on the right of the dancer##1
 8. the nurse is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking tea##2
11. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | 7up  | soy-milk   | tea         | coffee     | milk              | iced-tea    | almond-milk     |
| Job        | dancer | doctor | electrician | security-guard | paramedic | nurse | lawyer |

