.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, epic, musical, fantasy, martial-arts, animation, drama
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, subway, roller, airplane, train, ship
1. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person driving the ship and the person driving the airplane##2
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
9. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | fantasy     | animation | martial-arts | musical | drama  | crime |
| Transport     | subway | roller | airplane   | van     | ship    | snowmobile | train   |

