.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, almond-milk, lemonade, soy-milk, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, baking, skydiving, dancing, traveling, video-games, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is baking##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
9. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | sprite       | juice         | lemonade         | almond-milk   | iced-tea        | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | collecting | skydiving | reading | traveling | baking | video-games | dancing  |

