7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
