.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, romance, martial-arts, disaster, mystery, drama, action
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, jazz, techno, electronic, country, d&b
 1. the person watching crime movies is the fan of d&b##1
