 3. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the fan of funk##2
 4. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching action movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
 5. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 6. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of electronic##1
 9. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
10. the fan of techno is the person watching disaster movies##1

