 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the fan of r&b and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 4. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person drinking water##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
| Beverage      | juice   | water | milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk | cola   | coffee |
