 3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating cranberry##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 6. the person eating lime is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking grapefruitade is the person eating tomato##1
 8. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking mirinda and the person eating lime##2
10. the person drinking grapefruitade is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6    |   7    |
